cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with optimizing communication cost in content delivery networks. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also a likely category as load balancing is a key aspect of distributed systems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new meta-heuristic algorithm for load balancing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with optimizing a system (CDN) with multiple components (servers). 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the proposed algorithm is a variant of the bees algorithm, which is a type of swarm intelligence algorithm.
